# A dynamic rigid body sphere (thrown from the camera with key 9 in the App testbed).
# Collision masking demo: spheres are on the Debris layer and only collide with Default
# (ground, cubes), so thrown spheres pass through each other.
Prefab physicsSphere
	Component Render
		StaticMesh Sphere
	Component Physics
		Body Dynamic
		Shape Sphere
		Radius 0.5
		Friction 0.4
		Restitution 0.4
		Layer Debris
		CollidesWith Default
